name: Storiedmaps
body:
### Welcome to StoriedMaps, a customized [Open Outreach](https://www.drupal.org/project/openoutreach) Drupal distribution that makes it easy to create rich, community-focused, map-based web sites.
![StoriedMaps logo](https://www.drupal.org/files/project-images/storiedmaps_logo.png)
